Introduction

UNB (Korean: 유앤비; Japanese: ユアンビー) was a 9-member project group formed through a survival show called "The Unit". They made their official debut in April 2019 and disbanded in January 2019 with 2 mini albums.

The group consisted of familiar faces such as UKISS' Jun; Bigstar's Feeldog; Madtown's Daewon; H.B.Y's Marco; Hotshot's Hojung, Newkidd's Hansol, Bigflo's Euijin, A.C.E's Chan, and IM's Kijung.
